#: ../../source/electric-simulador-condensador.rst:9
msgid "El :index:`Condensador`"
msgstr "El: Index: `Capacitor`"

#: ../../source/electric-simulador-condensador.rst:10
msgid ""
"Un condensador es un componente que puede almacenar energía eléctrica igual "
"que lo hace una pila recargable, pero con dos diferencias. La energía "
"almacenada es mucho menor que la de una pila y los ciclos de carga y "
"descarga que soporta un condensador son de muchos miles de millones, "
"mientras que una pila recargable solo soporta pocos cientos de ciclos."
msgstr ""
"A capacitor is a component that can store electricity just like a "
"rechargeable battery does, but with two differences. The stored energy is "
"much lower than that of a battery and the loading and download cycles that "
"support a capacitor are many billions, while a rechargeable battery only "
"supports few hundred cycles."

